About this hotel

Set within the walled Ancient Medina district, this unpretentious hotel is an 8-minute walk from the Kasbah Museum. It's 2 km from both the Municipal Beach, and ferries at the Port of Tangier.

Check-in time: 2:00 PM
Check-out time: 12:00 PM

    Ancien Medina

    The walled Ancien Medina is entered through centuries-old gates, including Bab Al Bahr, which offers access to the ramparts for port views. The Tangier American Legation Museum traces local history, and there are displays of pottery and Roman relics in the Kasbah Museum, built around a courtyard. Alleys off Rue Siaghine are lined with shops selling rugs and spices, and lead to the landmark Grand Socco square.

    About this hotel

    Set within the walled Ancient Medina district, this unpretentious hotel is an 8-minute walk from the Kasbah Museum. It's 2 km from both the Municipal Beach, and ferries at the Port of Tangier. …

    Informal rooms feature Wi-Fi, TVs and minifridges. Some have balconies and/or views of the port. Family rooms can sleep up to 4 guests.

    Breakfast is served in an ornately decorated restaurant that features a terrace with port views.
